  "text": "(1) The function \u03d5 is permutation. [CITATION_1] The arithmetic Galois group G is the alternating group A 4 and the geometric Galois group N is the Klein four-group V 4 . (3) There exist u, v \u2208 F q 3 such that at least one between u, v does not lie in F q and the following factorization holds: R 3 (x) = (x \u2212 (ut + v))(x \u2212 (u q t + v q ))(x \u2212 (u q 2 t + v q 2 )).",
